{"tid":1345053,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連白粉報資深體育記者都開post屌何君堯","createTime":"2019-07-22T01:14:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T03:57:52.000Z","uid":36494,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6055a17e31b7f0b28add6a5435afaa7c1f525574","tid":1345053,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:14:03.000Z","msg":"大家都知白粉報係親政權建制<br />\n<br />\n佢旗下啲記者即使唔係親政權，平時都唔會開聲直屌建制<br />\n<br />\n呢個白粉資深體育記者同香港好多足球員都好熟，由以前李健和山度士到而家班現役球員都熟<br />\n<br />\n佢而家係白粉報體育版阿頭<br />\n<br />\n佢平時啲報導只講體育而不談政治<br />\n<br />\n但佢尋晚都出咗post屌何君堯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HfgEw0Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHfgEw0Y.png&h=7fcdd676&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"add2a88fe2a02cb933a284b7046b15c5dfee0f9f","tid":1345053,"uid":217433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:17:03.000Z","msg":"姓何呢條友做得太出面"},{"pid":"c45b3262dddb5afe37b687c47ec9aff0fe70a36e","tid":1345053,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:28:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"03c7ae916c38f077e1c21230c249e541c406c939","tid":1345053,"uid":92585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:57:52.000Z","msg":"推"}]}